## Feature: CLI Interface [ID=EO-05]

Expose all capabilities as a single `eva` CLI using commander.

### Story: Implement discover command [ID=EO-05-001]

`eva discover [--repo <path>] [--out <path>]`
Runs top-down + bottom-up discovery.

### Story: Implement reconcile command [ID=EO-05-002]

`eva reconcile [--repo <path>] [--in <path>] [--out <path>]`
Consumes discovery.json, emits reconciliation.json.

### Story: Implement compute-trust command [ID=EO-05-003]

`eva compute-trust [--repo <path>] [--recon <path>] [--out <path>]`

### Story: Implement generate-ado command [ID=EO-05-004]

`eva generate-ado [--repo <path>] [--discovery <path>] [--recon <path>] [--out <path>]`

### Story: Implement report command [ID=EO-05-005]

`eva report [--repo <path>]`
Prints coverage, gaps, trust score to console.

### Story: Implement audit command [ID=EO-05-007]

`eva audit [--repo <path>]`
Combined: discover + reconcile + compute-trust + report in one shot.
Eliminates 4-command pipeline; guarantees artifact freshness before scoring.

### Story: Implement scan-portfolio command [ID=EO-05-006]

`eva scan-portfolio [--portfolio <path>] [--filter <ids>]`
Audits all numbered EVA project folders under a root.
Prints a portfolio-wide MTI table with actions per project.

### Story: Implement init command [ID=EO-05-008] [IMPL]

`eva init [--repo <path>] [--yes] [--prefix <id>]`
Interactive onboarding wizard. Detects project structure, guides plan setup,
runs first audit to display initial MTI score. `--yes` = non-interactive defaults.

