## Feature: Reporting [ID=EO-06]

Human-readable + machine-readable outputs that feed EVA governance.

### Story: Human-readable console report [ID=EO-06-001]

Print: epic title, feature/story counts, coverage table, gap list, trust score + actions.

### Story: Evidence-ready .eva/ folder output [ID=EO-06-002]

All JSON outputs written to `.eva/` in the target repo.
Each file includes `meta.schema`, `meta.generated_at`, `meta.repo`.

