## Feature: 37-data-model Integration [ID=EO-08]

Allow 37-data-model API to invoke eva-veritas to validate that declared
objects (endpoints, screens, services) have real artifact evidence.

### Story: Add /model/admin/audit-repo endpoint to 37-data-model [ID=EO-08-001]

Proxy endpoint in 37-data-model that calls eva-veritas MCP `audit_repo` tool.
Input: `project_id` (e.g. `33-eva-brain-v2`).
Returns: standard veritas audit response.
Registered in model as endpoint `POST /model/admin/audit-repo`.

### Story: Document model integrity check pattern [ID=EO-08-002]

Add `docs/library/08-EVA-VERITAS-INTEGRATION.md` to 37-data-model library.
Describes: when to call audit, how to interpret gaps, how trust gates model commits.

