## Feature: 38-ado-poc Integration [ID=EO-09]

Allow 38-ado-poc ADO Command Center to auto-seed sprint PBIs from verified gap stories.

### Story: Add gap-to-PBI pipeline command [ID=EO-09-001]

`eva generate-ado --repo <path> --gaps-only` flag.
Filters ADO CSV to stories with gap tags only.
Designed to be consumed by 38-ado-poc sprint seeder.

### Story: Document 38-ado-poc integration pattern [ID=EO-09-002]

Add integration guide to 38-ado-poc: how to invoke eva-veritas, consume the CSV,
and prevent manually-invented PBIs from entering the sprint.

### Story: Import OpenAPI spec as plan source [ID=EO-09-003] [IMPL]

`src/lib/openapi-parser.js` — probes repo root and docs/ for openapi.json/yaml or swagger.json/yaml.
Converts OpenAPI 2/3 paths/operations into veritas features + stories.
Output shape: `{ features: [], stories: [] }` with 3-part IDs `{prefix}-{DOMAIN}-{seq}`.

### Story: Parse ADO export CSV as plan source [ID=EO-09-004] [IMPL]

`src/lib/ado-import.js` — parses Azure DevOps work-item export CSV.
Maps Work Item Type (Epic/Feature/User Story/Task) → veritas plan hierarchy.
Wires stories to features and tasks to stories via Parent column.

