## Feature: generate-plan Command [ID=EO-11]

Agent-driven plan inference from any doc format.
Allows repos to gain veritas governance without reformatting PLAN.md.

### Story: Implement infer-plan.js heuristic parser [ID=EO-11-001]

Reads Phase/Sprint/Feature/Story/checklist structure from any markdown.
Auto-generates IDs where [ID=...] not present.
Detects format: veritas-native | phase-sprint | free-form.

### Story: Implement generate-plan CLI command [ID=EO-11-002]

Nests stories under features in veritas-plan.json (eva.veritas-plan.v1).
Prints feature breakdown table after writing.
Supports --sync-model flag to push summary to EVA data model API.

### Story: Update discover.js to prefer veritas-plan.json [ID=EO-11-003]

Checks .eva/veritas-plan.json before calling parsePlan().
Flattens nested features[].stories[] to { features, stories } shape.
Logs format_detected on load.

### Story: Document generate-plan in README.md [ID=EO-11-004]

For Agents section: zero-friction onboarding, format detection table, source priority.
CLI Commands section: generate-plan entry with --prefix and --sync-model options.
Output Artifacts: veritas-plan.json schema block.
